</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Our pets are better than beastlord pets. That is not a myth that is a fact. They have more hp. They do more damage. They have more "utility". 
